'''Secrets''' in Robotrek include hidden items, optional content, and advanced mechanics.

== Secret Robots ==

=== Robot Appearance ===
Robots can be customized in appearance:
* Visit the inventor's house
* Use color items to change robot colors
* Multiple appearance options available

== Hidden Items ==

=== Sword Combinations ===
Combine items to create powerful weapons:
* Sword + Clean = Sword1
* Sword1 + Axe = Axe1
* Experimentation reveals more recipes

=== Secret Books ===
Programming books found throughout the game:
* Teach new robot abilities
* Hidden in dungeons and towns
* Some require solving puzzles

== Invention System ==

=== R&D Department ===
The Research & Development system allows creating items:
* Combine two items to create new ones
* Failed combinations waste materials
* Successful combinations unlock recipes

