== Optional Bosses ==

=== Hidden Boss Fights ===
Several optional boss encounters exist:
* Stronger versions of story bosses
* Unique rewards for defeating them
* Require backtracking to access

== Secret Areas ==

=== Volcano Cave ===
Contains rare materials for robot upgrades.

=== Ancient Ruins ===
Hidden dungeon with powerful equipment.

=== Robot Museum ===
Contains information about the game world and robots.

== Easter Eggs ==

=== Enix References ===
Various references to other Enix games appear:
* NPCs make references to Dragon Quest
* Some items reference other Enix properties

=== Developer Messages ===
Hidden messages from developers in certain areas:
* Check unusual objects
* Talk to NPCs multiple times

== Tips ==

'''Robot Building:'''
* Focus on one robot first
* Balance offense and defense
* Experiment with combinations

'''Inventory Management:'''
* Save powerful items for bosses
* Carry healing items always
* Combination materials fill inventory quickly

'''Combat:'''
* Learn enemy patterns
* Use appropriate robot for each area
* Grinding improves success rate

== Known Issues ==

=== Battery Save ===
* Game uses battery save
* Make backup saves when possible
* Corrupted saves lose all progress

=== Translation ===
* Some text abbreviated or unclear
* Certain items have confusing descriptions
* Combination recipes not always obvious

